<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a0167e2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s5610"><num value="5610">§ 5610.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this chapter, including to pay the United States contribution to the Organization as provided in Article IX of the Convention, $500,000 for each fiscal year through fiscal year 2021.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a0167e3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/43/tII/s211">Pub. L. 104–43, title II, § 211</ref>, <date date="1995-11-03">Nov. 3, 1995</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/109/382">109 Stat. 382</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/105/384/tII/s201/a">Pub. L. 105–384, title II, § 201(a)</ref>, <date date="1998-11-13">Nov. 13, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/3451">112 Stat. 3451</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/107/372/tIII/s305">Pub. L. 107–372, title III, § 305</ref>, <date date="2002-12-19">Dec. 19, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/3096">116 Stat. 3096</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/109/479/tIII/s302/i">Pub. L. 109–479, title III, § 302(i)</ref>, <date date="2007-01-12">Jan. 12, 2007</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3625">120 Stat. 3625</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/114/327/tV/s509">Pub. L. 114–327, title V, § 509</ref>, <date date="2016-12-16">Dec. 16, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/1998">130 Stat. 1998</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
